FINAL INSTRUCTION
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Generate comprehensive JSON summary of this earnings release. Preserve all management statements with full context. Report only what was explicitly stated. Use Three-Tier Inference Framework to minimize interpretation. Surface contradictions within the release. Scale naturally to release depth (1,500-3,000 words). Return valid, parseable JSON matching schema exactly.
